 2023-12212023-12-08NR, CRA
ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectCanada Revenue Agency - Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving that the Canada Revenue Agency enter into a collective agreement with the PROFESSIONAL INSTITUTE OF THE PUBLIC SERVICE OF CANADA that covers all employees by the Audit, Financial and Scientific Group bargaining unit for the period beginning on December 22, 2022 and ending on December 21, 2026.
